lisher = Tower Records | accessdate = 2012-12-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121220083057/https://tower.com/evita-madonna-dvd/wapi/107073279 }}</ref>。2012年6月19日，电影的15周年版[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]上市<ref>{{cite web | title = Evita Blu-ray: 15th Anniversary Edition | url = https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Evita-Blu-ray/40217/ | publisher = Blu-ray.com | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190411053028/https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Evita-Blu-ray/40217/ | archivedate = 2019-04-11 }}</ref>。蓝光光碟采用[[1080p|1080p]]高分辨率，包含院线预告片，{{單雙書名號轉換|你必须爱我}}的音乐视频，以及幕后制作纪录片《〈贝隆夫人〉拍摄记》（{{lang|en|The Making of ''Evita''}}）<ref name="EvitaBluRay" />。

== 反响 ==

=== 专业评价 ===
《贝隆夫人》所获评价褒贬不一<ref>{{cite web | title = Madonna's Hot Ticket: 'Evita' Close to No. 1 But Will Strong Box Office Get Material Girl Into H'wood Groove? | archivedate = 2018-07-23 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180723182235/http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/nydn-features/madonna-hot-ticket-evita-close-no-1-strong-box-office-material-girl-h-wood-groove-article-1.761206 | last = Dominguez | url = https://www.nydailynews.com/archives/nydn-features/madonna-hot-ticket-evita-close-no-1-strong-box-office-material-girl-h-wood-groove-article-1.761206 | first = Robert | newspaper = New York Daily News | date = 1997-01-14 | accessdate = 2020-08-30 }}</ref>。根据[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]收集的38篇评论文章，影片“新鲜度”63%，[[加權平均數|平均得分]]6.67（最高十分）。网站的共识评述写道：《贝隆夫人》的叙事层面有些缺乏说服力，但配乐着实出色，让这部以事实为依据的音乐剧有望达到史诗片的宏伟目标。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/evita | title = Evita (1996) | website = [[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]] | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200808081852/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/evita | archivedate = 2020-08-08 }}</ref>{{lang|en|[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]}}根据23份评论打出平均分45（最高100），表明“褒贬不一”<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.metacritic.com/movie/evita | title = Evita Reviews | website = Metacritic | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180905145402/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/evita | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2018-09-05 }}</ref>。[[影院评分|影院评分]]开展的观众调查打分为“{{lang|en|A}}-”（最高{{lang|en|A}}+，最低{{lang|en|F}}）<ref>需在“{{lang|en|FIND CINEMASCORE}}”下面的搜索框输入电影原名“Evita”，页面会自动显示评分：{{cite web | url = http://www.cinemascore.com/ | title = CinemaScore | work = [[影院评分|CinemaScore]] | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | archive-date = 2019-05-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190518162710/https://www.cinemascore.com/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

马尔科姆·约翰逊（{{lang|en|Malcolm Johnson}}）在《哈特福德新闻报》发文称：“尽管困难重重，这部长期延误的电影版最终成为导演艾伦·帕克和重生大明星麦当娜、新生代超级巨星安东尼奥·班德拉斯，以及经验丰厚的老将尊尼芬·帕斯爱的结晶”<ref>{{cite news | last = Johnson | first = Malcolm | date = 1997-01-10 | url = http://articles.courant.com/1997-01-10/features/9701100038_1_eva-peron-evita-che-guevara | title = Madonna Gives Soul to Screen Incarnation Of 'Evita' | work = Hartford Courant | accessdate = 2018-07-23 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180723183131/http://articles.courant.com/1997-01-10/features/9701100038_1_eva-peron-evita-che-guevara | archivedate = 2018-07-23 }}</ref>《芝加哥太阳报》刊登罗杰·伊伯特的文章，给予本片三星半好评（最高四星），称“帕克的视觉处理令音乐焕然一新，麦当娜和班德拉斯为电影带来激情。观众看完影片感到物有所值，而且艾薇塔在天之灵肯定也会这么想。”<ref>{{cite news | last = Ebert | first = Roger | url = https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/evita-1997 | title = Evita Movie Review & Film Summary (1997) | publisher = RogerEbert.com | date = 1997-01-03 | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2020-08-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200811063802/https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/evita-1997 }}</ref>此外，伊伯特和同事[[吉恩·西斯克|吉恩·西斯克]]（{{lang|en|Gene Siskel}}）在联播电视节目《[[电影_(1986年电视节目)|电影]]》（''{{lang|en|At the Movies}}''）中对本片的评分都是竖起大拇指<ref>{{cite video | people = Gene Siskel and Roger Ebert | title = Siskel & Ebert & the Movies | date = 1996-12-21}}</ref>。西斯克在《芝加哥太阳报》发表的影评称赞导演才能出众，电影场面壮观<ref>{{cite news | last = Siskel | first = Gene | url = https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1997-01-03-9701030243-story.html | title = Madonna Stands Up To 'Evita' Demands | newspaper = [[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]] | date = 1997-01-03 | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180723182539/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1997-01-03/entertainment/9701030243_1_evita-role-of-juan-peron-che-guevara | archivedate = 2018-07-23 }}</ref>。《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》的[[理查德·科利斯|理查德·科利斯]]（{{lang|en|Richard Corliss}}）指出，“《贝隆夫人》没有沦为漫长而复杂的音乐视频，每分每秒都像真正的电影，人物也值得我们投入感情或抱以最深切的怀疑”<ref>{{cite journal | last = Corliss | first = Richard | url = http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,985711,00.html | title = Cinema: Madona and Eva Peron: You Must Love Her | journal = Time | date = 1996-12-16 | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190626190633/http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,985711,00.html | archivedate = 2019-06-26 }}</ref>。影评人扎克·康纳（{{lang|en|Zach Conner}}）对电影表现“感到欣慰，无论表演还是制作都可圆可点，麦当娜再次超越大家的期望，她诠释的艾薇塔带着凄美的疲劳感，展现出足够份量的明星气质。所有人无论对麦当娜和伊娃是爱是恨，眼睛都会不由自主地聚焦在她身上”。<ref name="Taraborrelli-2008" />{{rp|285}}

[[有线电视新闻网|有线电视新闻网]]的卡罗尔·巴克兰（{{lang|en|Carol Buckland}}）认为，“《贝隆夫人》基本上就是有史诗抱负的音乐视频。这并不是说她的画面不华丽，或是娱乐效果偶尔不怎么样，实际情况恰恰相反。但即便整体气势恢宏，电影依然缺乏实质内容和灵魂。”<ref>{{cite news | last = Buckland | first = Carol | url = http://edition.cnn.com/SHOWBIZ/9701/04/evita.review/ | title = 'Evita' Tailor-made for Madonna | publisher = [[有线电视新闻网|CNN]] | date = 1997-01-04 | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200811063758/http://edition.cnn.com/SHOWBIZ/9701/04/evita.review/ | archivedate = 2020-08-11 }}</ref>大卫·安森（{{lang|en|David Ansen}}）在《[[新闻周刊|新闻周刊]]》发文称电影华丽壮观仿佛史诗，但看完后却无法让观众产生任何情感共鸣<ref name="Tangos" />。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》刊登[[欧文·格里伯曼|欧文·格里伯曼]]（{{lang|en|Owen Gleiberman}}）的评论，评分仅“{{lang|en|C}}-”（最高{{lang|en|A}}+），他批评导演处理失当，将本来能够从更大视角呈现的剧情局限在舞台范围，节奏缓慢而混乱，仿佛以20世纪70年代的平庸摇滚演绎“现实主义”拉美革命音乐视频<ref>{{cite news | last = Gleiberman | first = Owen | deadurl = no | url = https://ew.com/article/1996/12/20/evita-2/ | title = Evita | work = Entertainment Weekly | date = 1996-12-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200811063801/https://ew.com/article/1996/12/20/evita-2/ | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | archivedate = 2020-08-11 }}</ref>。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的[[珍妮特·马斯林|珍妮特·马斯林]]（{{lang|en|Janet Maslin}}）称赞麦当娜的演出，影片的服装设计和摄影，但感觉导演没有表露出任何道德或政治倾向，各个方向全力推进，有些不知节制，令观众筋疲力尽<ref>{{cite news | last = Maslin | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1996/12/25/movies/madonna-chic-pop-star-as-chic-political-star.html | title = Madonna, Chic Pop Star as Chic Political Star | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 1996-12-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200710042258/https://www.nytimes.com/1996/12/25/movies/madonna-chic-pop-star-as-chic-political-star.html | archivedate = 2020-07-10 | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | deadurl = no | first = Janet | page = C7 }}</ref>。简·霍维兹（{{lang|en|Jane Horwitz}}）在《[[太阳哨兵报|南佛罗里达太阳哨兵报]]》（''{{lang|en|South Florida Sun Sentinel}}''）发文称：“麦当娜的演唱很有说服力，表演也过得去，但缺乏深度、从容和力度。幸运的是，导演艾伦·帕克的拍摄手法立足历史，史诗般的群众场面和棕褐色的新闻纪录片风格让她看上去更加出彩”<ref>{{cite news | last = Horwitz | archivedate = 2019-04-04 | first = Jane | url = https://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/fl-xpm-1997-01-10-9701030337-story.html | title = Evita | newspaper = South Florida Sun Sentinel | date = 1997-01-10 | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190404172330/https://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/fl-xpm-1997-01-10-9701030337-story.html }}</ref>。《[[旧金山纪事报|旧金山纪事报]]》的芭芭拉·舒尔加瑟（{{lang|en|Barbara Shulgasser}}）对本片评价不佳，称电影本该聚焦政治、解放和腐败，下层阶级反抗压迫的胜利，但实际上却流于表面，思路简单，到最后根本没有任何意义<ref>{{cite news | last = Shulgasser | first = Barbara | title = Evita' eviscerated | archivedate = 2018-09-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180925065117/https://www.sfgate.com/style/article/Evita-eviscerated-3143555.php | url = https://www.sfgate.com/style/article/Evita-eviscerated-3143555.php | newspaper = [[旧金山纪事报|San Francisco Chronicle]] | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | date = 1997-01-01 }}</ref>。

=== 荣誉 ===
{{main|贝隆夫人获奖与提名列表}}
《贝隆夫人》获得众多奖项肯定，其中又以女主角、导演、配乐和歌曲{{單雙書名號轉換|你必须爱我}}最受认可。影片获五项[[金球獎|金球獎]]提名<ref>{{cite news | title = 'English Patient' Leads Golden Globe Nominations | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1996/12/20/arts/english-patient-leads-golden-globe-nominations.html | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 1996-12-20 | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200103234837/https://www.nytimes.com/1996/12/20/arts/english-patient-leads-golden-globe-nominations.html | archivedate = 2020-01-03 }}</ref>，最后三项胜出，分别是[[金球獎最佳音樂及喜劇電影|最佳影片（音乐剧/喜剧类）]]、[[金球獎最佳音樂及喜劇類電影女主角|最佳电影女主角（音乐剧/喜剧类）]]（麦当娜）和[[金球獎最佳原創歌曲|最佳原创歌曲]]（{{單雙書名號轉換|你必须爱我}}）<ref name="Globes">{{cite web | title = Winners & Nominees 1997 | url = https://www.goldenglobes.com/winners-nominees/1997 | publisher = [[金球獎|Golden Globe Award]]s | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2020-07-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200724203031/https://www.goldenglobes.com/winners-nominees/1997 }}</ref>。{{單雙書名號轉換|你必须爱我}}还在[[第69届奥斯卡金像奖|第69届奥斯卡金像奖]]角逐中夺得[[奥斯卡最佳原创歌曲奖|最佳原创歌曲奖]]，电影另获[[奥斯卡最佳影片剪辑奖|最佳剪辑]]、[[奧斯卡最佳攝影獎|最佳摄影]]、[[奥斯卡最佳艺术指导奖|最佳艺术指导]]和[[奥斯卡最佳音效奖|最佳音效]]四项提名<ref name="Oscars1997">{{Cite web | url = https://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/1997 | title = The 69th Academy Awards (1997) Nominees and Winners | publisher = Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200818051545/https://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/1997 | archivedate = 2020-08-18 }}</ref>，麦当娜在颁奖典礼上登台表演{{單雙書名號轉換|你必须爱我}}<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.eonline.com/news/34077/madonna-will-sing-at-the-oscars | title = Madonna Will Sing at the Oscars | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180816163653/https://www.eonline.com/news/34077/madonna-will-sing-at-the-oscars | first = Jeff | last = Copeland | date = 1997-02-12 | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | work = E! News | archivedate = 2018-08-16 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。[[国家评论协会|国家评论协会]]将本片列入1996年十大佳片，排名第四<ref>{{cite web | title = 1996 Archives – National Board of Review | url = https://nationalboardofreview.org/award-years/1996/ | publisher = [[國家評論協會|National Board of Review]] | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200817132551/https://nationalboardofreview.org/award-years/1996/ | archivedate = 2020-08-17 }}</ref>。《贝隆夫人》获[[第50届英国电影学院奖|第50届英国电影学院奖]]八项提名，但均未胜出<ref>{{cite web | url = http://awards.bafta.org/keyword-search?keywords=Evita | title = BAFTA Awards Search Box: Put 'Evita' and click | publisher = [[英国电影学院奖|British Academy Film Awards]] | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180612141951/http://awards.bafta.org/keyword-search?keywords=Evita | archivedate = 2018-06-12 }}</ref>，还在[[第一届金卫星奖|第一届金卫星奖]]角逐中获五项提名，最后拿下[[衛星獎最佳電影|最佳影片]]、[[金卫星奖最佳原创歌曲|最佳原创歌曲]]（{{單雙書名號轉換|你必须爱我}}）和[[金卫星奖最佳服装设计|最佳服装设计]]奖（佩妮·罗斯）<ref>{{cite news | title = Cruise Tops Golden Satellite Awards | url = https://www.eonline.com/news/33966/cruise-tops-golden-satellite-awards | work = E! News | first = Marcus | last = Errico | date = 1997-01-15 | accessdate = 2020-08-30 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2018-09-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180925025955/https://www.eonline.com/news/33966/cruise-tops-golden-satellite-awards }}</ref>。

